# Notebook Conventions

- The first cell is always the import cell. All `import` statements go there — never scatter imports across later cells.
- Import order: stdlib, then third-party, then local — alphabetically within each group (ruff-compatible).
- Notebooks are numbered and run in order; respect data dependencies between them.
- `F401` (unused imports) is intentionally ignored in notebooks — exploratory cells may import without using.
